RJkf00usnAyhL7ay1sVd2xQjErOJnO3fETYnhIEbQyun_0WMyumH17IxLOdhezioV8allZA8GjaqzC1VzQq2K0R5_AeFVY7dj5pYDysiZwk\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_rUqJV6LZuy9wtEaZ43Yk0rNO|fc_03f39fddca6188290169df2557378c8198aaeded8609a4236b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":36604,"output":194,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36798,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776231759943,"responseId":"resp_03f39fddca6188290169df255151ac8198bccf05088a2766bc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"545a18ad","parentId":"2caadbbb","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:42:48.243Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_rUqJV6LZuy9wtEaZ43Yk0rNO|fc_03f39fddca6188290169df2557378c8198aaeded8609a4236b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: ths-local-holdings\ndescription: \"Inspect Tonghuashun/同花顺真实持仓 from two sources: (1) the 10jqka 投资账本 web app (`tzzb.10jqka.com.cn`) when a reusable browser session or exported request is available, and (2) local macOS Tonghuashun app ledger files as a fail-closed fallback. Use when the user mentions 同花顺持仓、投资账本网页、10jqka tzzb 链接、同花顺 App、本地账本、多账户混仓、账本识别、真实持仓校准, or when reports/alerts are using the wrong holdings scope and you need a verified source instead of guessing.\"\n---\n\n# Ths Local Holdings\n\n优先把 **10jqka 投资账本网页** 当主源；只有网页 API / 登录态暂时拿不到时，才退回本机 `XcsLscjDataFile_*` 账本文件。\n核心原则不变：**宁可 fail closed，也不要猜主账号/猜主持仓。**\n\n## Workflow\n\n### 1. 先探测网页主源是否可用\n\n先运行：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py scan \\\n  --page-url 'https://tzzb.10jqka.com.cn/pc/index.html#/myAccount/a/C6QIQGQ' \\\n  --out /tmp/tzzb_web_probe.json\n```\n\n这一步会给出三类证据：\n- 前端 bundle 里是否存在 `/caishen_fund/...` API 路由\n- 本机 Chromium/Edge/Chrome profile 里是否存在 `tzzb.10jqka.com.cn` 历史、cookie、localStorage 痕迹\n- 当前环境是否缺少 Playwright / Selenium / 可自动化能力\n\n### 2. 最短路径：HAR / cURL → request-json\n\n如果用户能提供 **HAR** 或 **Copy as cURL**，先转成 request-json，再接 replay。\n\n#### 2.1 HAR 转 request-json\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py convert-har \\\n  --har /path/to/tzzb.har \\\n  --url-contains stock_position \\\n  --out /tmp/tzzb_stock_position_request.json\n```\n\n说明：\n- 默认优先挑选 URL 命中 `/caishen_fund/...` 已知接口的条目\n- 若 HAR 里命中多个条目，可加 `--url-contains stock_position` 或 `--entry-index 12`\n- 输出文件就是 replay 可直接消费的 `request-json`\n\n#### 2.2 cURL 转 request-json\n\n把浏览器 Network 里的 **Copy as cURL (bash)** 原样存成文本文件后运行：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py convert-curl \\\n  --curl-file /path/to/tzzb_stock_position.curl.txt \\\n  --out /tmp/tzzb_stock_position_request.json\n```\n\n也支持直接内联一条短 cURL：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py convert-curl \\\n  --curl \"curl 'https://tzzb.10jqka.com.cn/caishen_fund/pc/asset/v1/stock_position' -X POST ...\" \\\n  --out /tmp/tzzb_stock_position_request.json\n```\n\n目前转换器覆盖的常见字段：\n- URL / Method\n- `-H/--header`\n- `-b/--cookie` 或 `Cookie:` header\n- `-d/--data/--data-raw/--data-binary/--data-urlencode`\n- `-A/--user-agent`\n- `-e/--referer`\n- `-G/--get`\n\n### 3. 先 dry-run，再 replay\n\n先校验 request-json 是否成型：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py replay \\\n  --request-json /tmp/tzzb_stock_position_request.json \\\n  --out-dir /tmp/ths-web-holdings \\\n  --dry-run\n```\n\ndry-run 会输出：\n- `tzzb_request_preview.json`\n- 请求方法 / URL / header 名 / cookie 名 / body 类型摘要\n\n确认没问题后，再实际回放：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py replay \\\n  --request-json /tmp/tzzb_stock_position_request.json \\\n  --out-dir /tmp/ths-web-holdings\n```\n\n如果响应里含 `position` 数组，脚本会直接产出标准化的：\n- `ths_selected_holdings.csv`\n- `ths_selected_holdings.json`\n\n这两份文件就是给 selected holdings / sync 链路吃的统一格式。\n\n### 3.5 直接同步成 fusion-report 可自动发现的 selected holdings\n\n如果你已经有 replay 产物，可以再跑一步，把网页持仓同步成 `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json/csv`：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/sync_web_selected_holdings.py \\\n  --source-dir /tmp/ths-web-holdings \\\n  --out-dir /tmp/ths-web-selected\n```\n\n输出：\n- `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json`\n- `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.csv`\n- `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.meta.json`\n\n其中 `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json` 可被 `a-share-fusion-report` 直接 autodiscover 消费。\n\n### 4. 可以直接指导用户怎么发材料\n\n后续你可以直接让用户二选一：\n\n1. **发 HAR**\n   - 在 DevTools Network 导出 HAR\n   - 你这边跑 `convert-har -> replay --dry-run -> replay`\n\n2. **发 cURL**\n   - 在 DevTools Network 对成功请求点 `Copy as cURL (bash)`\n   - 保存成 `.curl.txt`\n   - 你这边跑 `convert-curl -> replay --dry-run -> replay`\n\n一句话操作模板：\n\n```bash\n# HAR\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py convert-har --har /path/to/tzzb.har --url-contains stock_position --out /tmp/tzzb_request.json\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py replay --request-json /tmp/tzzb_request.json --out-dir /tmp/ths-web-holdings --dry-run\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py replay --request-json /tmp/tzzb_request.json --out-dir /tmp/ths-web-holdings\n\n# cURL\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py convert-curl --curl-file /path/to/tzzb_stock_position.curl.txt --out /tmp/tzzb_request.json\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py replay --request-json /tmp/tzzb_request.json --out-dir /tmp/ths-web-holdings --dry-run\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py replay --request-json /tmp/tzzb_request.json --out-dir /tmp/ths-web-holdings\n```\n\n### 5. 网页主源暂时不可用时，再列本地账本\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_local_holdings.py list\n```\n\n这会输出：\n- 账本文件路径\n- `ledger_ids`\n- 每个账本的持仓摘要：A股 / 港股 / 基金 / 总数\n- 每个账本当前持仓代码列表\n\n如果只找到一个账本，可以直接导出。\n如果找到多个账本，**不要自动猜**；后续必须显式传 `--ledger-id` 或上游 selection config。\n\n### 6. 按指定 ledger id 导出本地账本持仓\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_local_holdings.py export \\\n  --ledger-id 2269916 \\\n  --stock-only \\\n  --out-dir /tmp/ths-holdings\n```\n\n默认输出：\n- `ths_selected_holdings.csv`\n- `ths_selected_holdings.json`\n\nJSON 会包含：\n- 选中的 ledger ids\n- 实际命中的账本文件\n- 持仓摘要\n- 逐条持仓明细\n\n### 7. 多账本/多来源场景下的硬规则\n\n- 发现多个账本时，**没有 `--ledger-id` / 显式 selection 就报错退出**。\n- 不要用“持仓数最多”“文件最新”“股票最多”去猜主账本。\n- 网页 localStorage 里即使看到了缓存持仓，也**只把它当证据，不直接接上游**；必须先拿到可验证的 API 请求/响应，或用户明确接受这个缓存口径。\n- 如果用户已经明确说某些股票**不是**她的持仓，用 `list` 输出反查它们属于哪个 ledger。\n- 如果用户要的是“只看股票”，加 `--stock-only`，把基金/ETF 剥掉。\n\n## Notes\n\n- 当前推荐的主源顺序：\n  1. **网页 API 成功回放并归一化后的 `ths_selected_holdings.*`**\n  2. **本地账本显式 ledger 导出**\n- `ths_tzzb_web_probe.py` 只负责探测/转换/回放/归一化；它不会伪造登录态，也不会假装抓取成功。\n- 默认扫描浏览器：Microsoft Edge / Google Chrome / Chromium（macOS）。\n- 如果后续要接入报告链路，优先让上游直接消费网页 API 归一化后的 `ths_selected_holdings.csv/json`；网页主源拿不到时，才退回本地 ledger 方案。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776231768222}}
