 or preferences. I think using a tool for verification will be the best approach, possibly with a script for testing. I'll explore how to access the page effectively.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Inspecting skill scripts**\\n\\nI need to take a closer look at the skill scripts or any related documents. It could be helpful to see if the script supports capturing requests. I'll focus on reading the relevant sections of the script to confirm this capability. Checking these details is essential, as they might guide me in implementing the right functionality. I want to ensure I gather all the necessary information before moving forward!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我继续往前跑一次，尽量直接验证“现有浏览器会话能不能拿到账本数据”。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03f39fddca6188290169df27162aa081989873bfe466383eae\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_k1FR3vDpLVgkzGXmcl2hVpCq|fc_03f39fddca6188290169df2716384481988e7bbf6669cfdd25","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py","offset":930,"limit":180},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py\",\"offset\":930,\"limit\":180}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":48765,"output":299,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49064,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776232199161,"responseId":"resp_03f39fddca6188290169df270929308198b5c12d74f0bf1498"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cda00c5b","parentId":"281f3558","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:50:15.864Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_k1FR3vDpLVgkzGXmcl2hVpCq|fc_03f39fddca6188290169df2716384481988e7bbf6669cfdd25","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n    result: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"status_code\": response.status_code,\n        \"content_type\": response.headers.get(\"content-type\", \"\"),\n        \"url\": response.url,\n        \"raw_response\": str(raw_path),\n    }\n\n    parsed_json: Any = None\n    try:\n        parsed_json = response.json()\n    except Exception:\n        parsed_json = None\n\n    if parsed_json is not None:\n        json_path = out_dir / \"tzzb_raw_response.json\"\n        json_path.write_text(json.dumps(parsed_json, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n        result[\"raw_json\"] = str(json_path)\n        holdings = parse_stock_position_payload(parsed_json, response.url, spec)\n        if holdings:\n            csv_path = out_dir / args.csv_name\n            normalized_json_path = out_dir / args.json_name\n            write_csv(csv_path, holdings)\n            normalized_json_path.write_text(\n                json.dumps(\n                    {\n                        \"source\": \"tzzb_web_stock_position_api\",\n                        \"request_json\": str(request_path),\n                        \"request_url\": response.url,\n                        \"status_code\": response.status_code,\n                        \"summary\": summarize_holdings(holdings),\n                        \"holdings\": [\n                            {\n                                \"symbol\": holding.symbol,\n                                \"asset_type\": holding.asset_type,\n                                \"name\": holding.name,\n                                \"quantity\": holding.quantity,\n                                \"cost_price\": holding.cost_price,\n                                \"source_path\": holding.source_path,\n                                \"ledger_ids\": holding.ledger_ids,\n                            }\n                            for holding in holdings\n                        ],\n                    },\n                    ensure_ascii=False,\n                    indent=2,\n                ),\n                encoding=\"utf-8\",\n            )\n            result[\"normalized_csv\"] = str(csv_path)\n            result[\"normalized_json\"] = str(normalized_json_path)\n            result[\"summary\"] = summarize_holdings(holdings)\n\n    print(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n    return 0 if response.ok else 1\n\n\ndef build_parser() -> argparse.ArgumentParser:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"探测/转换/回放同花顺投资账本网页 API 请求\")\n    sub = parser.add_subparsers(dest=\"command\", required=True)\n\n    scan_parser = sub.add_parser(\"scan\", help=\"扫描网页 bundle、浏览器 cookie/localStorage/history 痕迹\")\n    scan_parser.add_argument(\"--page-url\", default=DEFAULT_PAGE_URL, help=\"投资账本页面 URL\")\n    scan_parser.add_argument(\"--out\", default=\"\", help=\"输出 JSON 文件\")\n    scan_parser.set_defaults(func=cmd_scan)\n\n    convert_har_parser = sub.add_parser(\"convert-har\", help=\"把 HAR 中的请求条目转换成 request-json\")\n    convert_har_parser.add_argument(\"--har\", required=True, help=\"HAR 文件路径\")\n    convert_har_parser.add_argument(\"--out\", required=True, help=\"输出 request-json 文件\")\n    convert_har_parser.add_argument(\"--url-contains\", default=\"\", help=\"仅选择 URL 包含该片段的条目\")\n    convert_har_parser.add_argument(\"--entry-index\", type=int, default=-1, help=\"显式指定 HAR entry 下标\")\n    convert_har_parser.set_defaults(func=cmd_convert_har)\n\n    convert_curl_parser = sub.add_parser(\"convert-curl\", help=\"把 cURL 文本转换成 request-json\")\n    curl_source = convert_curl_parser.add_mutually_exclusive_group(required=True)\n    curl_source.add_argument(\"--curl\", default=\"\", help=\"直接传入 cURL 文本\")\n    curl_source.add_argument(\"--curl-file\", default=\"\", help=\"包含 cURL 文本的文件\")\n    convert_curl_parser.add_argument(\"--out\", required=True, help=\"输出 request-json 文件\")\n    convert_curl_parser.set_defaults(func=cmd_convert_curl)\n\n    replay_parser = sub.add_parser(\"replay\", help=\"用 request-json 回放 API，并尽量归一化持仓\")\n    replay_parser.add_argument(\"--request-json\", required=True, help=\"请求定义 JSON，包含 url/method/headers/cookies/data/json\")\n    replay_parser.add_argument(\"--out-dir\", default=\".\", help=\"输出目录\")\n    replay_parser.add_argument(\"--csv-name\", default=\"ths_selected_holdings.csv\", help=\"归一化 CSV 文件名\")\n    replay_parser.add_argument(\"--json-name\", default=\"ths_selected_holdings.json\", help=\"归一化 JSON 文件名\")\n    replay_parser.add_argument(\"--dry-run\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"只校验 request-json 与预览，不实际发请求\")\n    replay_parser.set_defaults(func=cmd_replay)\n\n    return parser\n\n\ndef main() -> int:\n    parser = build_parser()\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n    return int(args.func(args))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    raise SystemExit(main())\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776232215845}}
