{"type":"message","id":"6c13997a","parentId":"4cf04b0f","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:51:40.263Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_knktMxjeJP6SKa42ACCL7sgN|fc_03f39fddca6188290169df276b16c48198b928dbd8e0b4f3b4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"copied_to\": \"/var/folders/9d/zc1kgqs14dq00fd1z3n2f_kw0000gn/T/edge-ths-qfm56ise/UserData\",\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"final_url\": \"https://tzzb.10jqka.com.cn/pc/index.html#/unlogin\",\n  \"title\": \"投资账本-专业的股票基金记账，盈亏分析工具\",\n  \"content_snippet\": \"同花顺旗下投资复盘工具\\n盈亏复盘、收益统计、对比分析一站式查看\\niOS端\\nAndroid端\\n浏览器插件\\n多种方式导入持仓，灵活配置表头体验更佳\\n账本APP端账户数据支持展示至网页端，大屏查看更方便\\n通过交割单批量导入历史流水，支持手动调整持仓数据\\n灵活配置表头，支持包括持仓盈亏、当日盈亏、本月盈亏、累计盈亏、成本价和回本涨幅等多种统计项及分析\\n多个账户统一管理，汇总持仓查看更方便\\n支持多个账户同时展示，便捷查看各账户资产及收益\\n支持“汇总编辑”功能，自定义选择您想要汇总的账户\\n多账户持仓数据汇总，方便查看同一股票或基金的汇总持仓数量和收益情况\\n专业资产分析，丰富的图表及盈亏可视化\\n支持查看不同时间阶段的收益走势，了解您的账户在不同市场环境中的表现\\n利用盈亏日历功能让您精准掌握每日、每月和每年的收益情况\\n个股盈亏排行，支持找到这段时间为您赚最多和亏最多的股票\\n支持多个账户收益曲线同屏展示，对比不同账户的阶段表现\\n自动生成投资周报，帮您复盘本周操作\\n每周系统会自动生成投资周报，详细记录账户的收益变化和每日盈亏金额\\n交易操作分析，统计本周交易股票的数量、成功率和行业偏好等数据，帮助您全面复盘\\n支持查看历史周报，回顾当时的市场情况和投资表现\\n投资账本 · PC谷歌浏览器插件\\n上班摸鱼看涨跌有着落啦！\\n· 插件安装流程 ·\\n1.下载 插件压缩包(.zip格式)，并解压缩\\n2.打开谷歌浏览器，复制chrome://extensions/并粘贴到地址栏，按回车键\\n3.在右上角打开开发者模式\\n4.点击左上角按钮，选择第1步解压的文件夹，即可安装完成\\nCopyright Zhejiang RoyalFlush Network Technology Co., Ltd. All rights reserved. 浙江同花顺网络科技有限公司版权所有 浙ICP备10056399号-3\",\n  \"cookie_names\": [\n    \"v\"\n  ],\n  \"cookie_count\": 1\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776232300246}}
{"type":"message","id":"2dc4822c","parentId":"6c13997a","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:51:52.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Examining Edge session persistence**\n\nI'm concluding that the stored profile copy doesn’t preserve authenticated sessions. Just having the current live Edge on disk isn't enough either. It seems like the running Edge might hold the in-memory session. I could ask the user to keep their browser open or maybe manually export cURL data. I’m curious about using AppleScript to inspect the current page state through Edge tabs. Can I execute JavaScript on the active tab or a specific URL? Let’s check more about that!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_03f39fddca6188290169df276fab288198b939e856e87e5b86\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp3yd3qU6icsf3XXZsfJGV2prTkWUqYiL1_Rb7Nio1OzQtNBKqq_zQWW6RbCnyTWWFbDKo5h6Wnoa2ZrN6bV6otO2SIo49eSlUsM2HUaHL1uDyraXdCLGfzrbZd5QXdr3x9K-MtKg_7psvsRYyVU1CB4f130Gcj2u6FbiTrGSTNZRvhYomAKClxx9N0SUJFVwwbCZcpY_9JOcd4-0Uer4a9M2q6QwEXGQwSrSY5VuHcoPM9GrbSJx3fC2zMdM-IjtT36ERdiqn9IN9EXp32vRthcHSiHoOk2hn9oqjQkTvcPLtkfngg9bcgkmtPyNKpSBuQujHEuZZ8UJgBpvWZVhTOkAxYggZGqFPW9tvpkxCt5WUNAbc4_0N55yomtVI-0fM4BckhShln6cQjv73rNWXWe1Nd1yez-RoqnsOwK6ZJCPOugmTD5Qwm56F6RJOASRF0uw-Cc6b_LBTgBrEw1RQqBUqqa_GSCjkdrzIc2Ot2lP4rAzEeVKy0n5qUxff3lBz0oJjcKE-NipuCv9y0rvvrW0WfKnIyJOi1og_te02_Ok477w_YPomekhXHdE3Zf7ph734RMaTFl_WS_5zzXI9YSqB99innkM8RAGcvmbksgEl8pqZ5p8XsFZrHV1gHc4xbno16bkP4z2_Din0SILjFhxQDjt6WLjeLp-IXyus-Q7AcVG8ng5shgNF8dtHpb7v4DE0733sXcv5-xj8WpFB-ZDLD13leD5ZqfpuTgZyAFIVoJIpSfBQNW1SKddtfikMjE0IY5MYnssUG45PR4d-CkcJoFxftKEMEr69KtyxSUOWbrLZkNsnZ6gKbGsKO9Pyb8huZ2X0eEm3Bs0Wu8CrHrIIZMUXjUBxUINwArWdt1uhbB1F1rhz0DhtIy2mQPcZvV7Sqm9dCDgWXsPk92itvlT4DGo20bnheyS368eVYAn64KW51U_1d2EbDAAEvYMSCBCe1F9e0rTP_k-NiYiF-eIEGIYlpo82J0eqgs7cCHX0szVUIttklCooQT96FvdHSym2WrhXhn_Ug1wmV4i6mxklip9M26ibmsdlDvJvIkaZorRWR6dvofpgbhH8OSw0HRJYOtEsB9XC0LAqPX1UFkq4b63h30pR95MzS6g7U7buCvXmp48EBa1K19_OzVDFoZ7pi0nxsEvdHfUXTOD