\\nI'm concluding that the stored profile copy doesn’t preserve authenticated sessions. Just having the current live Edge on disk isn't enough either. It seems like the running Edge might hold the in-memory session. I could ask the user to keep their browser open or maybe manually export cURL data. I’m curious about using AppleScript to inspect the current page state through Edge tabs. Can I execute JavaScript on the active tab or a specific URL? Let’s check more about that!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我再补一刀：看能不能从**正在运行的 Edge**里拿到当前打开的投资账本页状态；如果拿不到，就说明只能走导出请求这条路了。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03f39fddca6188290169df2777d0348198b6af9297fcb9707c\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2RLVULvM4BK2IrxgOPNL5FyY|fc_03f39fddca6188290169df2777e6c48198af55f77e0fcdfb06","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"osascript -e 'tell application \"Microsoft Edge\" to get {name, URL} of every tab of every window'","timeout":30,"workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"osascript -e 'tell application \\\"Microsoft Edge\\\" to get {name, URL} of every tab of every window'\",\"timeout\":30,\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":53553,"output":440,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776232300264,"responseId":"resp_03f39fddca6188290169df276dd9e88198b19f460d7fd79f64"}}
